@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083
@memberBaseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@internalSecret = your_internal_service_secret_key_here
@productId = aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  사전 준비 (member-service 필요)
###
###  member-service(8081) + order-service(8083) 동시 기동 필수
###  Kafka(29092) 기동 필수
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 0-1. 회원가입
POST {{memberBaseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "order-test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@",
  "name": "주문테스트",
  "phone": "01012345678"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("memberId", response.body.data.memberId);
%}


### STEP 0-2. 예치금 충전 (100,000원)
POST {{memberBaseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/charge
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 100000
}


### STEP 0-3. 배송지 등록
POST {{memberBaseUrl}}/member/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "recipient": "홍길동",
  "phone": "01012345678",
  "zipcode": "06236",
  "address1": "서울시 강남구",
  "address2": "101호",
  "isDefault": true
}

> {%
  client.global.set("addressId", response.body.data.addressId);
%}


### STEP 0-4. 장바구니에 상품 추가
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/cart/item
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

> {%
  client.global.set("cartItemId", response.body.data.cartItemId);
%}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 1. 결제 페이지 조회 (Checkout)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 1-1. 장바구니 경유 checkout
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/checkout?cartItemIds={{cartItemId}}
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 1-2. 바로구매 checkout
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/checkout?productId={{productId}}&quantity=1
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 2. 주문 생성
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 2-1. 장바구니 경유 주문 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 2,
      "cartItemId": "{{cartItemId}}"
    }
  ],
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("orderId", response.body.data.orderId);
%}


### STEP 2-2. 바로구매 주문 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}"
}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 3. 주문 후 검증
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 3-1. 예치금 잔액 확인 (100000 - 30000 - 15000 = 55000)
GET {{memberBaseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 3-2. 장바구니 비어있는지 확인 (주문 후 자동 삭제)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/cart
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 4. 주문 조회 (3순위)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 4-1. 주문 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/order
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 4-2. 주문 목록 - 상태 필터
GET {{baseUrl}}/order?status=PAID
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 4-3. 주문 목록 - 페이징
GET {{baseUrl}}/order?page=0&size=1
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 4-4. 주문 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 5. 주문 취소 (3순위)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 5-1. 주문 취소
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 5-2. 취소 후 상태 확인 (CANCELLED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 5-3. 취소 후 예치금 복원 확인
GET {{memberBaseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 6. 구매확정 (4순위)
###
###  주의: 구매확정은 DELIVERED 상태에서만 가능.
###  테스트 전 DB에서 상태를 변경하세요:
###  UPDATE orders SET status = 'DELIVERED', delivered_at = NOW() WHERE id = '<orderId>';
###  UPDATE order_item SET status = 'DELIVERED' WHERE order_id = '<orderId>';
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 6-1. 구매확정
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/confirm
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 6-2. 구매확정 후 상태 확인 (PURCHASE_CONFIRMED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 7. 배송 관리 (5순위)
###
###  STEP 2에서 생성한 2번째 주문 사용.
###  DB에서 DELIVERED 상태로 변경 후 테스트.
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 7-1. 송장 등록
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/shipment
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "carrier": "CJ대한통운",
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "shipmentStatus": "SHIPPED"
}


### STEP 7-2. 배송 상태 변경 → IN_TRANSIT
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/shipment
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "carrier": "CJ대한통운",
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "shipmentStatus": "IN_TRANSIT"
}


### STEP 7-3. 배송 상태 변경 → DELIVERED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/shipment
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "carrier": "CJ대한통운",
  "trackingNumber": "1234567890",
  "shipmentStatus": "DELIVERED"
}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 8. 반품 신청 (5순위)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 8-1. 반품 신청 (DELIVERED 상태에서)
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/return
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "reason": "상품 불량",
  "orderItemIds": ["{{orderItemId2}}"]
}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  실패 케이스
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### [실패] 인증 없이 checkout → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/checkout?productId={{productId}}&quantity=1


### [실패] 인증 없이 주문 생성 → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [{"productId": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 1}],
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}"
}


### [실패] 예치금 부족 주문 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "items": [{"productId": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 100}],
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}"
}


### [실패] 빈 주문 항목 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "items": [],
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}"
}


### [실패] 인증 없이 주문 목록 → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/order


### [실패] 존재하지 않는 주문 상세 → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] 이미 취소된 주문 재취소 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] 다른 회원의 주문 조회 → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}
X-User-Id: 99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999
X-Role: USER


### [실패] CANCELLED 필터 조회 (취소 건 1개 확인)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order?status=CANCELLED
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] PAID 상태에서 구매확정 → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/confirm
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] 이미 구매확정된 주문 재확정 → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/confirm
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] 다른 회원이 구매확정 → 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/confirm
X-User-Id: 99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999
X-Role: USER


### [실패] PAID 상태에서 반품 신청 → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId}}/return
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "reason": "테스트",
  "orderItemIds": ["{{orderItemId2}}"]
}


### [실패] 배송 필수값 누락 → 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/shipment
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "carrier": "",
  "trackingNumber": ""
}


### [실패] 반품 사유 누락 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/{{orderId2}}/return
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "reason": "",
  "orderItemIds": []
}
